{"tid":210923,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想對付件老屎忽","createTime":"2017-04-21T09:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T14:02:17.000Z","uid":60630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ad94d60f0089fc7f235d4e87c822fc2f4bd1d5","tid":210923,"uid":60630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:27:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我就係港島做緊sales<br />\n有件老屎忽聲稱做左十幾年，但某d商品完全唔撚識賣，推灑比我做，我做左唔夠半年已經識賣啦，算<br />\n但最近佢成日將我賣過既單話自己做，同老闆領功<br />\n所以我想陰佢一獲，我知佢賣某d商品果陣，係有違商品說明條例，對某件商品作出不實既陳述<br />\n我想問係咪直接報海關，扮係客詳細咁講件事出黎，咁海關就會放蛇做野？另外有冇得匿名舉報？"},{"pid":"2e8e7767b238b5a8a9672426fd0440392eb588e9","tid":210923,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969b4d8793c84f945c8486594a8bc51f38c4a6d0","tid":210923,"uid":87380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cb0a31bbb7ecc0815ba723ad79d3aa97c7f233","tid":210923,"uid":60630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:45:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2c6b9f4b3683ea1601d08ab25ba658e493b55e","tid":210923,"uid":4849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></